{"tid":1769274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［12月8］汝欲和平，必先備戰，全民帶防裝！","createTime":"2019-12-04T18:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T07:05:31.000Z","uid":145847,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c66746534d402f0374854d5d9768a41b1d6454b1","tid":1769274,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"此話出自拉丁文格言，Si vis pacem, para bellum<br />\n意思為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［和平條件往往建立在做好必要發動戰爭的準備上。］</span></span></strong><br />\n見呢幾日鬼登有風吹唔好帶裝，我唔反對，你可能練過鐡布衫，鐡頭功，咁就唔洗驚。<br />\n但你可能好似我咁係一個普通學生哥、一個打工仔、一個退休人士，咁你就可能要帶返個盔，帶個豬咀、風鏡會好啲，甚至乎護膝、肘，走得甩人冇事先做到世界冠軍。<br />\n咩話？有人同你講帶裝係比藉口佢放tg?睇尼你無咩記性，上星期遊行行行下都無端放煙，Bob 叔都食埋，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢要放煙係唔洗藉口㗎傻豬豬！</span></span></strong><br />\n唔帶裝，班狗就笑住咁放煙玩paintball，心唸今次你仲唔仆街，笑我地傻仔。<br />\n你帶住裝，起馬都攩到吓，唔洗麻煩fa，又唔洗爆江，防裝又入唔到你罪。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">藉口？你會唔會斥責個女仔比人強奸係因為著得性感？</span></strong>唔會呀嘛，同樣道理，帶防裝啦！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有裝先有和平既資本！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"76ce464823f67972e81a9b8b4f32de37293a6019","tid":1769274,"uid":222071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T18:26:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0345e43f748e4beacbd4c49d45dc867becbbd5a7","tid":1769274,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"49dc82f6c0f8ba3c616cf41075ce05bd7d94f79b","tid":1769274,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T18:27:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"462851cd3e0076c674f2a042d84724648a090503","tid":1769274,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aec3f4ffc5e53049f1e43988c042f23ed005bdac","tid":1769274,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T18:27:35.000Z","msg":"P